pageProduct.name: Sukin Brightening Glow Night Moisturiser Jar 50ml
pageProduct.description:
Â 

General Information

Rejuvenate Your Skin Overnight With Our Australian Bioactive Complex, Kakadu Plum And Vitamin E.

Warnings

Avoid Contact With Eyes. If Irritation Occurs Rinse Immediately And Discontinue Use. For External Use Only.

Common Uses

Kakadu Plum, A Natural Source Of Vitamin C, Vitamin E And Australian Bioactive Complex Rich In Antioxidants Brighten And Plump Skin To Rejuvenate Your Complexion Overnight. With A Blend Of Mango Butter And Squalane To Deeply Hydrate And Promote Natural Glow, Whilst Helping To Prevent Damage Caused By Environmental Stressors.

Ingredients

Ingredients: Water (Aqua), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Cetyl Alcohol, Decyl Oleate, Ceteareth-20, Hydrolyzed Sunflower Seed Wax, Bromelain, Terminalia Ferdinandiana Fruit Extract (Kakadu Plum), Squalane, Mangifera Indica (Mango) Seed Butter, Ananas Sativus (Pineapple) Fruit Extract, Carica Papaya (Papaya) Fruit Extract, Mangifera Indica (Mango) Fruit Extract, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Extract, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Glucose, Citric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Tromethamine, Fragrance (Parfum)*, Citral**, Limonene** *Natural Fragrance **Component Of Natural Fragrance

Directions

After Cleansing At Night, Gently Massage Into Face, Neck And Decolletage, Using Gentle, Upward Motions.
